document_data.name: Nyssa Seebenstern
document_data.mainbody: '''Nyssa Seebenstern''' was a caravan leader in the [[Dalelands]].
document_data.Personality: Nyssa was full of enthusiasm and idealism.
document_data.History:
Nyssa was a woman of [[Thesk|Theskian]] ancestry. She was well known in the Dalelands for her caravans.

In [[1479 DR]], while traveling with her caravan to [[Daggerdale]], Nyssa was attacked by [[gnoll]] raiders.
